## Pipeline

```
SwitchParams matrix (~100 configs)
        ▼
   Chisel elaboration
        ▼
   SystemVerilog
        ▼
   Verilator sim ──► fitness metrics
        ▼        └─► waveforms
        ▼        └─► saturating traffic
        ▼        └─► conflicting traffic
        ▼
   FitnessTable ──► sort by fitness
                └─► inspect the gap metrics
```

