## The config matrix

The product of the `SwitchParams` architecture axes (`spac/hw/Types.scala`):

| Axis | Values |
|------|--------|
| `hash` | FullLookup, MultiBankHash |
| `buf` | NxNVOQ, SharedVOQ |
| `sched` | RoundRobin, ISLIP, EDRRM |
| `nPorts` | {2, 4, 8, 16, ...} (final set TBD) |
| (width/depth) | held fixed unless an axis is promoted |

2 × 2 × 3 = 12 architectural variants per port count. We may vary the exact port-count set and
whether we promote `dataBits`/`qDepthLog`.

