## Milestones

- **M1 — RTL core.** Done (carried from V1). Chisel switch + Verilator functional
  tests pass (12/12).
- **M2 — Sweep harness.** SV emit + Verilator sweep over the matrix, recording the
  fitness metrics.
- **M3 — Logical II + II gap.** Static logical-II analyzer; wire practical II from
  M2; compute and rank on the gap.
- **M4 — Ranking.** FitnessTable → sorted report; inspect the II-gap and fitness
  spread across the matrix.

