## Immediate next step

Characterize 2–3 representative configs end to end: emit SystemVerilog, run the
Verilator sweep (real throughput/latency/practical II, including a conflict
pattern), compute logical II by hand, and look at the gap. That grounds the II
contract (open decision 2) and tells us whether the metrics behave as SPAC's did
before we scale to the full matrix.